    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Level 24</p><p>Focus Beacon</p><p>Starting at 24th level, the base use of your Ki-Borne Awareness feature does not expend Focus points. You must still expend Focus points to extend your truesight beyond 30 feet as a bonus action. This increase lasts for a minute or until you are incapacitated.</p><p>Improved World Strike</p><p>When you reach 24th level, your World Strike damage calculation is increased to 7d8 x 5, or 9d8 x 5 on a critical hit.</p><p>Soulful Recovery</p><p>At 24th level, when you use the Recover action, you regain 5 Focus points.</p></div>",
